{"tid":143703,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"學神重考天光道求救","createTime":"2017-03-04T19:42:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-09T00:53:38.000Z","uid":59167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8e0c296f3dcf7c9fe8628a6a375b9f16c601f411","tid":143703,"uid":59167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T19:42:22.000Z","msg":"想問下如果行靠背壟道洗唔洗上三波 師傅話唔洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n學個時多數前面有車上唔到<br />\n同埋想問行亞皆老皆除左落完斜轉左後上一上3波仲有無位要上?<br />\n下星期考 好驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"235a78c4fe12afd0c84cb0b36e7f899d8a8e947c","tid":143703,"uid":59167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T19:42:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd3af24da82c2d03645453287cdb57836e652da0","tid":143703,"uid":31631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T19:43:41.000Z","msg":"上唔上三波真係睇路面情況"},{"pid":"03dc60431d141a4dc491d8bbf901fdb6cb803440","tid":143703,"uid":2764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T23:35:55.000Z","msg":"上3波係睇路面情況<br />\n前面大直路又冇乜車都唔上3波咪比人剔未使用適當波段<br />\n你師父擺撚到明想你肥補鐘啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實上3波可以好快<br />\n1波完起步放手制即上2波<br />\n踩深少少又3波<br />\n其實唔係要快 只要順就得<br />\n<br />\n利申：第2take 背壟pass<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6694c3919058904eb94bcc569581f1558026d2e","tid":143703,"uid":3242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T23:40:08.000Z","msg":"都係個句,要睇路面情況.<br />\n小車既話,可以30kmh 上三波, 上完無耐就可以轉灣前落番二波"},{"pid":"990c990155ca5edcd086e23148f047221af8edc3","tid":143703,"uid":68896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T23:45:08.000Z","msg":"成個路試一定要上正次3波<br />\n個師父咁同你講都有既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6106c1f426cd41daacce6db85deca022f2b06344","tid":143703,"uid":53133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T23:53:23.000Z","msg":"師傅考車唔洗上3波呢句都講得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 草定錢考過啦ching"},{"pid":"8a904597b10cbc0d6fe8e23ae880a109fc169cc7","tid":143703,"uid":9105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T00:03:07.000Z","msg":"一定要上3波 臨尾翻試場條大直路夠哂長比你上一上3波<br />\n調完頭轉彎落長命斜前 有夠路比你上一次 <br />\n2次機會 一定上到"},{"pid":"980bfee2c855c2eefaab50585148590da9eb5561","tid":143703,"uid":59167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T19:32:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一定要上3波 臨尾翻試場條大直路夠哂長比你上一上3波<br />\n調完頭轉彎落長命斜前 有夠路比你上一次 <br />\n2次機會 一定上到</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cffda0d88621982e969239b44510f87341be5bf","tid":143703,"uid":59167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T10:01:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一定要上3波 臨尾翻試場條大直路夠哂長比你上一上3波<br />\n調完頭轉彎落長命斜前 有夠路比你上一次 <br />\n2次機會 一定上到</blockquote><br />\n石鼓街轉左入常盛街好無上三波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實係咪只要夠車速 上一陣三波落返二波好過唔上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />adore#"},{"pid":"8d6d7454329ce8ecff0c0d6c85edf6620ff169cb","tid":143703,"uid":32859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T10:04:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一定要上3波 臨尾翻試場條大直路夠哂長比你上一上3波<br />\n調完頭轉彎落長命斜前 有夠路比你上一次 <br />\n2次機會 一定上到</blockquote><br />\n石鼓街轉左入常盛街好無上三波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實係咪只要夠車速 上一陣三波落返二波好過唔上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />adore#</blockquote><br />\n睇技術 唔chok就無問題 上斜落斜3波基本上無問題"},{"pid":"d6bd2dd97d41dd6afa6e7bc93f59d9e14d9b1fde","tid":143703,"uid":59167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T10:47:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>一定要上3波 臨尾翻試場條大直路夠哂長比你上一上3波<br />\n調完頭轉彎落長命斜前 有夠路比你上一次 <br />\n2次機會 一定上到</blockquote><br />\n石鼓街轉左入常盛街好無上三波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實係咪只要夠車速 上一陣三波落返二波好過唔上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />adore#</blockquote><br />\n睇技術 唔chok就無問題 上斜落斜3波基本上無問題</blockquote><br />\n行左四堂 次次美善同道都有死車搞到上唔到3波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3efa1350ca8bc567961b1e66e89aa999edcfe36c","tid":143703,"uid":1067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T10:49:18.000Z","msg":"上得到三波就要上，大塞車就無計啦"},{"pid":"8a8ef3cf127687839d38d2d72ab355fe3cb3f52a","tid":143703,"uid":13543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T12:44:31.000Z","msg":"條路有位有距離就要上3波<br />\n入左靠背壟道如果有機會其實一來一回係上到3波<br />\n再者返試場cut左右線之後都有機會上3波 但距離短d"},{"pid":"2524ef24872d945c1d46568e159ae8fcff148916","tid":143703,"uid":52062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T12:50:14.000Z","msg":"除左大塞,唔係一定要上,試過岩岩學車俾師傅屌唔上3波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0feb91435c81b175f5dd5767070859d96e65e8be","tid":143703,"uid":59167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T13:02:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>除左大塞,唔係一定要上,試過岩岩學車俾師傅屌唔上3波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打師傅話咩位置一定要上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b21cd3368d0c71d078daf8d50eb54214e2959e9","tid":143703,"uid":59167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T10:44:49.000Z","msg":"今日行靠背壟全程2波 8細tick pass<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d5ce929925c6353e01fc16b57215e7dd8e1e12f","tid":143703,"uid":44489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T11:16:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今日行靠背壟全程2波 8細tick pass<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n今日好多車上唔到3波？"},{"pid":"57241a763d204c9e84a214604e7dbbd953447d37","tid":143703,"uid":59167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T17:53:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>今日行靠背壟全程2波 8細tick pass<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n今日好多車上唔到3波？</blockquote><br />\n唔算太多 但美善同左右都有車泊 前面有學神"},{"pid":"3becc9f1df8de1334964e3bdf90fc7c0a7bff975","tid":143703,"uid":73935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T17:55:42.000Z","msg":"重考完有黃紙睇都唔知要做咩？"},{"pid":"1133c8c853bf677ac980b90ab1262b36677b45b1","tid":143703,"uid":59167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T19:31:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>重考完有黃紙睇都唔知要做咩？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efdb55728017cc82b9bece236d25cf470435f784","tid":143703,"uid":7980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T00:53:38.000Z","msg":"次次燈位起步，如果要轉彎既話<br />\n係彎心收油個下已經上埋個2波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 跟住就睇路況上唔上3波<br />\n學車係去學熟架車，而唔係死記去到乜野位去做乜野，你咁樣一有突發事就肥硬<br />\n你套功夫學得熟，有信心，有咩突發事都考唔到你<br />\n我考天光個陣有行人突然衝出黎要急停，又係大彎落斜個陣突然有死車要停車越過佢，後面仲要有一堆車黎緊<br />\n最後都1take pass"}]}